edu.ucdavis.cstars.client.layers

Class ArcGISTiledMapServiceLayer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.gwt.core.client.JavaScriptObject
      • edu.ucdavis.cstars.client.layers.Layer
        • edu.ucdavis.cstars.client.layers.TiledMapServiceLayer
          • edu.ucdavis.cstars.client.layers.ArcGISTiledMapServiceLayer

  • public class ArcGISTiledMapServiceLayer
extends TiledMapServiceLayer
    Allows you to work with a cached map service resource exposed by the ArcGIS Server REST API. A cached service accesses tiles from a cache instead of dynamically rendering images. For dynamic map services, see DynamicMapServiceLayer.
    Author:
    Justin Merz
